room_title: Escape room "Jewel Heist" by Urban Escape Games in Atlanta
room_address: 20 Mansell Court East, Suite #275, Alpharetta, GA 30076
room_description: The world's most valuable diamond was stolen just days ago by a mysterious lady in black. People are calling her the greatest thief of the century. Will you knock her off that pedestal by doing the impossible? Sneak into her mansion, complete the jewel heist and escape before she catches you!
